                        <a href="{{ path('faq') }}#social-insurance-and-reward-pot" class="d-none d-md-block btn btn-primary btn-block-xs mx-auto mb-5">I have more Q's</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div id="what-is-the-reward-pot" class="expanding-cardbox expanding-cardbox-white mb-4">
                        <div class="expanding-cardbox__body">
                            <h3 class="h5 expanding-cardbox__title text-zaffre mb-0">
                                What is the Reward Pot? <i class="far fa-chevron-down text-dodger-blue fa-lg"></i>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="expanding-cardbox__expand text-zaffre mt-4">
                                <p id="what-is-the-reward-pot-text">The reward pot is basically a <mark>group no claims bonus</mark>. For each person that buys insurance with us and connects together, for example You buy a policy and invite your mum to buy. She buys a policy and then you connect, each of you receive up to &pound;10 into your reward pots.</p>

                                <div class="h6">4 people connected to you = &pound;40 in your reward pot, &pound;10 in each of theirs.</div>

                                <div class="h6">8 people connected = &pound;80 in your reward pot, &pound;10 in each of theirs.</div>

                                <p class="mb-0">If neither you nor your connected friends claim, we will payout to you the value of your reward pot at the end of the policy year.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expanding-cardbox expanding-cardbox-white mb-4">
