                            <h3 class="h5 expanding-cardbox__title text-zaffre mb-0">
                                Is the money back with the reward pot guaranteed? <i class="far fa-chevron-down text-dodger-blue fa-lg"></i>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="expanding-cardbox__expand text-zaffre mt-4">
                                It depends on if you and your social circle make a claim. If none of you claim the money is guaranteed, however if someone makes a claim there may be no money left in the reward pot.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expanding-cardbox expanding-cardbox-white mb-4">
                        <div class="expanding-cardbox__body">
                            <h3 class="h5 expanding-cardbox__title text-zaffre mb-0">
                                Can anyone connect to anyone? <i class="far fa-chevron-down text-dodger-blue fa-lg"></i>
                            </h3>
                            <div class="expanding-cardbox__expand text-zaffre mt-4">
                                Yes, that is the beauty of social insurance, you can have as many connections as they like until your reward pot is worth 80% of the value of your insurance premium. For example if policy is &pound;100, you can have maximum 8 connections (&pound;80 / 80%).
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expanding-cardbox expanding-cardbox-white mb-4">
